  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 7 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "And 7 people took refuge in the refugee camp",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the ongoing economic crisis in the country, 7 more Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200breached Dhanushkodi in Tamil Nadu this morning.",
        "116 Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bhave gone to Dhanushkodi as refugees from Sri Lanka since last March.",
        "In this case, Mary Akashta (44) from Navarguzhi, Jaffna District, Sri Lanka, her two children, Mahesan (39) from Ananthapuri, Trikonamalai District, his wife Devi (38), and their two children, a total of 7 people left Sri Lanka by boat and arrived at the fifth sand dune area near Dhanushkodi this morning. reached",
        "On being informed, the Mandapam Coast Guard rescued the 5 Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bfrom the sandbar by boat and brought them to Dhanushkodi Arichalmunya shore and handed them over to the Rameswaram Marine Police.",
        "Also, the number of refugees from Sri Lanka who came to Tamil Nadu has increased to 123."
      ],
